<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Form::setName() allows subforms to be named '0' and even explicitly checks them with (empty() || === '0'). Zend_Form::getElementsBelongTo() uses getName() with empty() but does not check if name === '0'.</p>

<p>The result is data corruption in Zend_Form::getValues() because it uses getElementsBelongTo() for all subForms.</p>

    </div>
</div>

